The Learn Mode identifies different screens, such as History, Settings, and Main Screen, based on their design. You can use the thumbs-up button to mark a screen as "good" and the thumbs-down button to mark it as "bad." To remove a screen from a category, simply click the corresponding button again. If you press and hold a button, the screen will be immediately added to your desired category. The settings button provides additional options for customization. The current filter results are displayed above the buttons, and a blue background indicates that the screen has been learned but not yet saved.
